                                    <locus from="109ara" to="109avb"/>
                                   <desc type="GuestText">Unidentified Amharic treatise.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="am"><seg part="I">ይኽ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ አትመን፡ ይላል፡ ክብር፡ ለምን፡ የሚያልፍን፡ አውቆ፡ በምድር፡ የዓለም፡ ቆሙ፡ ሐጭር፡
                                    ለተመለከተው፡ አይመላም፡ ስዝር፡ ያንሳል፡ ከጽፍር፡ ከስንዴ፡ ከአተር፡ ከጤፍ፡ ከምስር፡ ምንም፡ ቢቈጽሩ፡ አይመላም፡ አስር፡ ይቀራል፡ ቢዢምር፡ የዓለም፡ ቆሙ፡ 
                                    ሐጭር፤</seg></q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="e1">
                                    <desc>The names of  the original owners <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13766TaklaG">Takla Giyorgis</persName>
                                        and <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13767Aqlisya">ʾAqlisyā</persName> are mentioned in supplications 
                                        throughout (e.g. <locus target="#10v #19r #104r #108v"/>), occasionally together with the name of the scribe,
                                        <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13769Petros">Ṗeṭros</persName> (e.g. <locus target="#35v #62v"/>), 
                                        but were then erased and that of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13768Abulides">ʾAbulidǝs</persName>. </desc>
                                </item>
                            </list>
                        </additions>
